 "last_comment_author": "MontrealMaxwell", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.bizpacreview.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZMMLmmR.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.bizpacreview.com/2026/04/11/rep-anna-paulina-luna-demands-swalwell-resign-from-congress-key-dem-joins-chorus-1632094/", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Rep. Anna Paulina Luna demands Swalwell RESIGN from Congress \u2013 key Dem joins chorus", "last_comment_created": 1776009615559, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 30, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "The California gubernatorial campaign of Rep. Eric Swalwell (D-Calif.) has gone up in flames over serious allegations of sexual assault by multiple women, and calls have already [\u2026]", "large_image": "UrRyFAYmN6E9VM1s.png", "title": "Rep. Anna Paulina Luna demands Swalwell RESIGN from Congress \u2013 key Dem joins chorus"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZMMMKsb", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 19, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8553849, "raw_content": "Jim Carrey wrote himself a check for 10 million dollars and dated it well into the future: November 1996.  He was able to cash the check after making Dumb and Dumber.\n\nThere are many other stories about people who have a clear vision.  \n\nSpend 10 minutes visualizing the image using all senses: sight, touch, scent, taste, and hearing.  Walk through the space as if you are there and see everything in vivid detail.  Repeat 3, 2, 1 in order to enter alpha wave length.\n\nDo this 10 minutes every day.\n\nIf you are going to be visualizing anyway, you may as well visualize what you want.  Stay away from the media and movies because then you are visualizing what they want.", "author": "tpactionchasethevote", "created": 1776017577232, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DresdenFirebomber", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Visualize clearly what you want (and not what they want).", "last_comment_created": 1776022606465, "content": "<p>Jim Carrey wrote himself a check for 10 million dollars and dated it well into the future: November 1996.  He was able to cash the check after making Dumb and Dumber.</p>\n<p>There are many other stories about people who have a clear vision.</p>\n<p>Spend 10 minutes visualizing the image using all senses: sight, touch, scent, taste, and hearing.  Walk through the space as if you are there and see everything in vivid detail.  Repeat 3, 2, 1 in order to enter alpha wave length.</p>\n<p>Do this 10 minutes every day.</p>\n<p>If you are going to be visualizing anyway, you may as well visualize what you want.  Stay away from the media and movies because then you are visualizing what they want.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 19, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZMMMbrP", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 17, "suggest